snippet.textDisplay: Please make a video speaking on eating disorders. I know as someone who has struggled with bulimia, exercise addiction, and anorexia, but is painted as a popular & perfect girl, younger girls in my highschool or even girls my age constantly ask me how I got the body I did, and how they wish they could have it. But it’s just unattainable if you’re treating your body well. I find myself looking at you and wondering how I try so so hard and I still can’t have the body you do. Please speak up you can break the glass ceiling truly
